<h2>2 · Why Separate the Data? 🤔</h2>
<p>We keep the level as a list of numbers (<code>LEVEL_1</code>) instead of writing each <code>pygame.Rect(...)</code> by hand in the loop.</p>
<p><strong>Give one reason this makes it easier to build <em>many</em> levels later.</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

